snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls: Blades Nintendo Switch Gameplay - Nintendo Treehouse: Live | E3 2019
snippet.description:
In this live demonstration from E3 2019, we’ll explore a dungeon in The Elder Scrolls: Blades while showcasing the game’s first ever controller support.

Follow Nintendo E3 coverage: http://e3.nintendo.com
